verbose_text: The results showed that the protein expression level of CRF was markedly increased in the hypothalamus (XREF_FIG) and duodenum (XREF_FIG) of FD rats, compared with the control group (hypothalamus : 0.38 +/-0.01 vs. 0.09 +/-0.01; P < 0.01) (duodenum : 0.27 +/-0.02 vs. 0.11 +/-0.02, P < 0.01).
